data.description: Show home with lots available! Open daily from 12-6 & Saturdays from 10-6! Come take a look at these new homes & all the incredible options! Spacious living & dining areas off of the kitchen. Master suite boasts a large walk-in closet. Quality features abound w/ granite kitchen countertops, 2x6 construction & front yard landscaping. Model is loaded w/ upgrades including a gourmet kitchen, bench in owner's entry & gas fireplace. Expand living space w/ finished basement option. Windsor schools!!! Check out the 3D Virtual Tour!!!
